{"id":146622,"xmlId":"com.mallowigi.colorHighlighter","name":"Color Highlighter","description":"\n    <h1>Color Highlighter</h1>\n    <h2>Highlight Colors in your IDE</h2>\n    \n    <div>\n      <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/src/main/resources/META-INF/pluginIcon.png\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"256\">\n    </div>\n    \n\n    <p>This plugin highlights colors in editors in order to make them stand out in your code.</p>\n    <br>\n    <p>This does the same as \"Show CSS Color preview as background\", only for more languages!</p>\n    <br>\n    <p>Currently supported languages:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>XML</li>\n      <li>HTML</li>\n      <li>JavaScript</li>\n      <li>TypeScript</li>\n      <li>Properties</li>\n      <li>YAML</li>\n      <li>Python</li>\n      <li>PHP</li>\n      <li>Ruby</li>\n      <li>Scala</li>\n      <li>Java</li>\n      <li>Kotlin</li>\n      <li>Objective-C</li>\n      <li>Swift</li>\n      <li>C</li>\n      <li>C++</li>\n      <li>C#</li>\n      <li>Markdown</li>\n    </ul>\n    <br>\n\n    \n    <h2>Features</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Preview most common color formats:</li>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Hex: <code>(#rgb, #rrggbb, #rrggbbaa)</code></li>\n        <li>RGB <code>rgb(red, green, blue[, alpha])</code></li>\n        <li>HSL <code>hsl(hue, saturation, luminance[, alpha])</code></li>\n        <li>0x <code>0xRRGGBBAA</code></li>\n        <li>Java/Kotlin Color function <code>[new ]Color(r, g, b)</code></li>\n        <li>Java/Kotlin Color properties <code>Color.XXXX</code></li>\n        <li>C# Color methods <code>Color.FromArgb(red, green, blue)</code></li>\n        <li>Web Colors <code>(red, green, khaki, goldenrod...)</code></li>\n        <li>FlatUI Colors <code>(emerald, carrot, amethyst...)</code></li>\n        <li><strong>Custom Colors (define your own custom colors!)</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n      <li>Also displays the color in the gutter, with options to <strong>copy to clipboard in different\n        formats!</strong></li>\n    </ul>\n    <br>\n\n    <h2>Donate</h2>\n    <p>This theme is backed up by <a href=\"https://opencollective.com/atom-material-themes-and-plugins\">OpenCollective</a>.\n      If you like this plugin, don't hesitate to\n      give it a star or donate via <a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/mallowigi\">Paypal</a> or <a href=\"https://opencollective.com/atom-material-themes-and-plugins#sponsor\">OpenCollective</a></p>\n    <br>\n\n    <h2>Screenshots</h2>\n\n    <h3>PHP</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/php.png\" alt=\"PHP\">\n\n\n    <h3>Python</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/python.png\" alt=\"Python\">\n\n\n    <h4>Ruby</h4>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/ruby.png\" alt=\"Ruby\">\n\n\n    <h4>Go</h4>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/go.png\" alt=\"Go\">\n\n\n    <h3>Objective C</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/objc.png\" alt=\"ObjectiveC\">\n\n\n    <h3>Swift</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/swift.png\" alt=\"Swift\">\n\n\n    <h3>JavaScript</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/js.png\" alt=\"JavaScript\">\n\n\n    <h3>Kotlin</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/kotlin.png\" alt=\"Kotlin\">\n\n\n    <h3>Java</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/java.png\" alt=\"Java\">\n\n\n    <h3>JSON</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/json.png\" alt=\"JSON\">\n\n\n    <h3>Properties</h3>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter/master/docs/screens/properties.png\" alt=\"Properties\">","organization":"Atom Material Themes & Plugins","tags":["Editor"],"vendor":"Atom Material Themes & Plugins","version":"9.2.0","dependencies":["com.intellij.modules.platform"],"optionalDependencies":["com.intellij.modules.lang","com.intellij.java","org.jetbrains.plugins.yaml","com.intellij.modules.json","org.jetbrains.plugins.ruby","com.intellij.properties","org.jetbrains.kotlin","com.jetbrains.php","org.intellij.scala","com.intellij.modules.python","com.intellij.modules.go-capable","com.intellij.modules.cidr.lang","org.intellij.plugins.markdown","com.intellij.modules.rider"],"since":"212.0","until":"214.*","sourceCodeUrl":"https://github.com/mallowigi/color-highlighter","size":2555109}